---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Luis Leon Pineda">
  <section class="page-header container">
    <p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
    <h1>Building reliable systems from concept through validation</h1>
  </section>

  <article class="about-page container">
    <div class="about-introduction">
      <div class="about-photo-wrapper">
        <img
          class="about-photo"
          src="/images/headshot/Luis.jpeg"
          alt="Professional headshot of Luis Leon Pineda"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="about-summary">
      <p>
        I am an electrical engineer with hands-on experience developing,
        integrating, and validating FPGA-based systems, embedded platforms,
        mixed-signal electronics, and board-level hardware. My work has included
        AMD/Xilinx Zynq-7000 platforms, SystemVerilog development, AXI-based
        peripheral integration, embedded C and C++, and FPGA hardware bring-up.
      </p>

      <p>
        I have designed, assembled, and tested mixed-signal PCBs for biomedical data
        acquisition, performed system-level debugging with oscilloscopes and logic
        analyzers, and developed repeatable verification procedures for both
        simulation and physical hardware. My previous automotive experience also
        strengthened my skills in electrical diagnostics, root-cause analysis,
        component integration, and post-repair validation.
      </p>

      <p>
        I enjoy working across the full engineering lifecycle, from requirements,
        design, and prototyping through integration, testing, documentation, and
        deployment. I have also led an eight-person senior design team in developing
        an educational FPGA platform, managing system integration, bitstream
        releases, hardware validation, and technical documentation.
      </p>  
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Core Skills</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Building and debugging digital systems with SystemVerilog and Verilog</li>
        <li>Designing, integrating, and verifying FPGA-based systems</li>
        <li>Working with Zynq-7000 devices and ARM-based embedded platforms</li>
        <li>Connecting and controlling hardware through AXI4 and AXI4-Lite</li>
        <li>Developing embedded applications in C and C++</li>
        <li>Designing PCBs and bringing new hardware prototypes to life</li>
        <li>Using oscilloscopes and logic analyzers to troubleshoot hardware</li>
        <li>Working with Vivado, Vitis, XSim, KiCad, LTspice, and MATLAB</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section awards-section">
      <h2>Awards & Recognition</h2>

      <div class="award-grid">
        <article class="award-card award-card-featured">
          <div class="award-featured-layout">
            <img
              class="award-image"
              src="/images/Group_pic_Industry_Choice.jpeg"
              alt="Industry Choice award recognition photo"
            />

            <div class="award-content">
              <p class="award-year">2026</p>
              <h3>Industry Choice Electrical Engineering</h3>
              <p>
                Recognized by visiting industry professionals as the top capstone project at the senior design showcase.
              </p>
              <p class="award-link">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/txstengineering_last-tuesday-isoe-hosted-our-annual-senior-ugcPost-7460824669852635136-u2j-?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAABKLeDIBtFDcGh2MiMe20QwA1iJjVNKxVFA" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                  View school post
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="award-card">
          <p class="award-year">Spring 2025</p>
          <h3>Dean's List</h3>
          <p>
            Named to the Dean’s List for outstanding academic performance
            during the Spring 2025 semester.
          </p>
          <p class="award-link">
            <a href="https://txstate.meritpages.com/stories/Luis-Leon-Pineda-Named-to-Texas-State-University-s-Spring-2025-Dean-s-List/167204610?" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              View Merit Pages profile
            </a>
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="award-card">
          <p class="award-year">Fall 2025</p>
          <h3>Dean's List</h3>
          <p>
            Named to the Dean’s List for outstanding academic performance
            during the Fall 2025 semester.
          </p>
          <p class="award-link">
            <a href="https://txstate.meritpages.com/stories/Luis-Leon-Pineda-of-Wimberley-Named-to-Texas-State-University-s-Fall-2025-Dean-s-List/177016992?" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              View Merit Pages profile
            </a>
          </p>
        </article>

      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>